    <div class="container" id="full_div">
        <h1 class="text-center text-decoration-underline border border-dark fw-bold"
        style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;">Help</h1>

        <h1>Welcome to the Help Center!
        </h1>
        <p>We’re here to guide you through any questions or challenges you may encounter while using our blog website.
            Below, you’ll find answers to common questions, along with tips to help you make the most of your
            experience.</p>


        <div id="helpAccordion" class="accordion">

            <!-- Item 1 -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                    <h2 class="mb-0">
                        <button class="btn btn-link" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne"
                            aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                            How to Create a Blog Post?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#helpAccordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        1. Log in to your account. <br>
                        2. Navigate to the “Create Post” section from your dashboard. <br>
                        3. Fill in the title, content, and any tags related to your post. <br>
                        4. Optionally, upload images to enhance your post. <br>
                        5. Click "Publish" to make your post live, or "Save Draft" to come back later.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 2 -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                    <h2 class="mb-0">
                        <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                            data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                            How Do I Edit or Delete a Post?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#helpAccordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        1. To edit a post, go to your profile, find the post, and click “Edit.”<br>
                        2. To delete a post, click the "Delete" button next to the post.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 3 -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                    <h2 class="mb-0">
                        <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                            data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                            How Can I Comment on a Post?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#helpAccordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <ol type="1">
                            <li>Ensure you’re logged in.</li>
                            <li>Scroll down to the comments section of any blog post.</li>
                            <li>Enter your comment in the text box and click "Submit." Your comment will appear below
                                the
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Add more items as needed -->
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingfour">
                    <h2 class="mb-0">
                        <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                            data-target="#collapsefour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                            How to Follow Other Bloggers?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div id="collapsefour" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingfour" data-parent="#helpAccordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <ol type="1">
                            <li>Visiting their profile page.</li>
                            <li>Clicking the “Follow” button. You'll get notified when they publish new content.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingfive">
                    <h2 class="mb-0">
                        <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                            data-target="#collapsefive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapsefive">
                            What to Do If I Forget My Password?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div id="collapsefive" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingfive" data-parent="#helpAccordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <ol type="1">
                            <li>Go to the login page and click on “Forgot Password.”</li>
                            <li>Enter your email address, and we’ll send a link to reset your password.
                            </li>
                            <li>Follow the instructions in the email to set a new password.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingsix">
                    <h2 class="mb-0">
                        <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                            data-target="#collapsesix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapsesix">
                            How to Customize My Profile?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div id="collapsesix" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingsix" data-parent="#helpAccordion">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <ol type="1">
                            <li>Logging in to your account.</li>
                            <li>Navigating to the “Profile” section.</li>
                            <li>From there, you can update your bio, profile picture, and any personal details.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card ">
                <div class="card-header" id="headingseven">
                    <h2 class="mb-0">
                        <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                            data-target="#collapseseven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseseven">
                            How to Report Issues or Contact Support?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div id="collapseseven" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingseven" data-parent="#helpAccordion">
                    <div class="card-body pb-3 mb-3">
                        <ol type="1">
                            <li>You can contact our support team via the “Contact Us” page.</li>
                            <li>Alternatively, send us an email at <a
                                    href="mailto:sblogify@gmail.com">sblogify@gmail.com</a>, and we’ll respond within
                                24-48 hours.
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
